{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1320042, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一大半比如说？", "timestamp": 1616516678, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320050, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "……", "timestamp": 1616516794, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320063, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "数学本来就是某种传承智慧的文科，附带研究形式的功能，真要比起来和研究语言的哲学没啥本质区别，只能说后者人才还没有被资本主义生产过程像压榨数学人才一样系统化", "timestamp": 1616516863, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320065, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "压榨", "timestamp": 1616516875, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320073, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "除了一些分析课程有点用外，剩下代数和几何系列的课程几乎都属于审美课程", "timestamp": 1616516941, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320085, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "任何一个专业开的专业课不都大多用来自嗨，实际很难用的到。。。", "timestamp": 1616517000, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320089, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 到也不是，很多数论也很有用处", "timestamp": 1616517020, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320092, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "数学这么多分支，为什么要说的和哲学一样？\n分析学、代数学、几何学、概率统计学、计算学、运筹学，哪一项是没有应用纯粹自嗨？", "timestamp": 1616517059, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320103, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这种说法就和“买菜用得着微积分吗”的说法一样，觉得没用只是没用到", "timestamp": 1616517177, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320106, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 哲学也不算是纯粹自嗨好吗……只是哲学的应用难以被当成意识形态宣传，在公共舆论之中不会显现而已…", "timestamp": 1616517211, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320111, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 比如对社会结构的分析啥的 感觉还是很需要哲学的 还有医学伦理问题", "timestamp": 1616517254, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320123, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 算是我对哲学的片面认识，我道歉。\n不过我的本意是数学有很应用的领域（比如统计学），并不完全都是研究形式的，因此将数学描述成研究形式的学科并不恰当。", "timestamp": 1616517367, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320130, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 这就是统计分出的原因啊——", "timestamp": 1616517413, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320132, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我也不是想说哲学就是自嗨，是在我的印象中哲学基本就是研究形式的学科", "timestamp": 1616517419, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320140, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 无论如何 数学的来历不是其被需要 而是人类对自身形式和逻辑的好奇，其本身注定是有存在价值的。Alice的问题可能是把所谓的应用当成人类社会的唯一的价值，这大概是某种资本主义思想）", "timestamp": 1616517495, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320151, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 嘛 其实我也不大懂 但是研究形式的大概不是逻辑就是数学吧", "timestamp": 1616517552, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320160, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: Alice快睡！", "timestamp": 1616517590, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2601384, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 259666, "reply_to": 1320140, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: bob说得对", "timestamp": 1632655778, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 259666, "reply": 18, "tag": null, "text": "#259588\n感觉数学系开的数学一大半只能自嗨", "timestamp": 1616516463, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1632655781, "url": "", "vote": {}}}